	<title>Calc freeze when copy down cell</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">When I copy down a cell, calc freeze.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">I must then kill calc with the app manager of windows because it is not possible to access the menu of libreoffice.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.3">Then I lose all my work made after the previous save.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.4">The system is not affected.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.5">The bug happen even with a small number of cell.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.6">It does not seems to happen with a normal copy and paste.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.7">This bug happend also with previous versions of libreoffice and openoffice.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.8">There is no surge in memory use and processor use.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
